{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "To uncover potential upstream regulators of these TFs, we visualize smooth gene expression trends of top-ranked lineage-correlated genes of the endoderm trajectory in a heatmap and sorted genes according to their peak in CytoTRACE pseudotime (Fig. 3e).",
    "We found LINC00458, LINC01356, NODAL and nine TFs to peak before FOXA2 and SOX17.",
    "All are known mouse endodermal development genes 33, 34 and our prediction that LINC00458 expression peaks before LINC01356 has also been observed previously 33.",
    "CellRank 2's CytoTRACEKernel allowed us to infer cellular dynamics from a snapshot of endoderm development without having to specify an initial state for pseudotime computation.",
    "We recovered terminal states, known driver genes and their temporal activation pattern."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "All are known mouse endodermal development genes 33, 34 and our prediction that LINC00458 expression peaks before LINC01356 has also been observed previously 33."
  ]
}